    <item>
      <title>卡斯皮银行主导的网上零售贷款业务受到哈萨克斯坦监管机构的审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/kaspi-led-online-retail-lending-draws-kazakh-watchdog-s-scrutiny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈萨克斯坦蓬勃发展的在线市场之所以蓬勃发展，部分原因在于一种受欢迎的融资方式，由于担心通胀和不断增加的消费者债务负担，这种融资方式目前受到监管机构的审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/kaspi-led-online-retail-lending-draws-kazakh-watchdog-s-scrutiny</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者要求印度储备银行允许将国债以零息债券形式出售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/investors-ask-rbi-to-let-state-debt-be-sold-as-zero-coupon-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，投资者敦促印度储备银行允许将州政府债务转为零息债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/investors-ask-rbi-to-let-state-debt-be-sold-as-zero-coupon-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 03:10:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通资产管理公司称中国市场以“更加乐观”的情绪结束今年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-10/china-markets-ending-year-with-more-optimism-jpm-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通资产管理公司的 Tai Hui 表示，中国金融市场“在年底前将更加乐观”。这是继北京方面最近承诺采取更大胆的经济刺激措施之后的又一举措。Hui 还表示，“中国股市的估值仍然相当有吸引力。”他在彭博电视上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-10/china-markets-ending-year-with-more-optimism-jpm-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 02:50:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受政策推动，中国债券收益率有望降至 1.5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/traders-see-china-yield-fall-to-1-5-on-everything-rally-hope</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国明年将转向宽松的货币政策，这引发了人们看涨的押注，即中国主权债务收益率将从历史低点进一步下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/traders-see-china-yield-fall-to-1-5-on-everything-rally-hope</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 01:49:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高层领导暗示将推出更大胆刺激措施 中国股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/chinese-stocks-rally-after-top-leaders-signal-bolder-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国高层领导人做出多年来最强有力的恢复经济增长的承诺后，中国股市周二上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/chinese-stocks-rally-after-top-leaders-signal-bolder-stimulus</guid>
